整条目"]],"\nresult, err := ai.AutoAdjustCourse(s.ctx, ai.AutoAdjustCourseInput{\n    Title:   info.Title,\n    Content: content,\n})"]]]],["$","p",{},["拿到 items 列表后，后续处理完全回归到确定性的代码逻辑 —— 将每条记录的日期字符串映射到所在学期，并计算出对应的周次和星期，最终构造出 ",["$","code",{},["model.AutoAdjustCourse"]]," 准备存入数据库："]],["$","pre",{},[["$","code",{"class":"hljs go"},[["$","span",{"class":"hljs-comment"},["// 根据 from_date 查找所属学期"]],"\nterm, found := utils.FindTermByDate(calendar.Terms, fromDate)\n\n",["$","span",{"class":"hljs-comment"},["// 计算 from_date 在该学期中对应的周次和星期几"]],"\nfromWeek, fromWeekday, err := utils.GetWeekdayByDate(term.StartDate, item.FromDate)\n\n",["$","span",{"class":"hljs-comment"},["// 构造最终数据"]],"\nadjustCourse := &model.AutoAdjustCourse{\n    Year:        year,\n    FromDate:    item.FromDate,\n    ToDate:      toDate,\n    Term:        term.Term,\n    FromWeek:    ",["$","span",{"class":"hljs-type"},["int64"]],"(fromWeek),\n    ToWeek:      toWeekPtr,\n    FromWeekday: ",["$","span",{"class":"hljs-type"},["int64"]],"(fromWeekday),\n    ToWeekday:   toWeekdayPtr,\n    Enabled:     ",["$","span",{"class":"hljs-literal"},["false"]],", ",["$","span",{"class":"hljs-comment"},["// 默认禁用，等待人工审核后再启用"]],"\n}"]]]],["$","p",{},["所有记录写入完成后，统一刷新涉及学期的缓存，确保后续的课表查询能立即感知到新的调课记录。"]],["$","h3",{"id":"应用调课规则"},["应用调课规则"]],["$","p",{},["调课记录写入数据库并启用之后，在学生请求课表时，系统在拿到原始课程数据后，紧接着读取当前学期所有已启用的调课记录，并通过 ",["$","code",{},["getAdjustRules"]]," 生成匹配的调课规则，生成最终应用到课程上的 ",["$","code",{},["CourseAdjustRule"]]," 列表："]],["$","pre",{},[["$","code",{"class":"hljs go"},["autoAdjustCourses, err := s.GetAutoAdjustCourseList(req.Term)\n\n",["$","span",{"class":"hljs-keyword"},["for"]]," _, c := ",["$","span",{"class":"hljs-keyword"},["range"]]," courses {\n    adjustRules := getAdjustRules(c.ScheduleRules, autoAdjustCourses)\n    c.ScheduleRules = jwch.ApplyAdjustRules(\n        jwch.ApplyAdjustRules(c.ScheduleRules, c.AdjustRules),\n        adjustRules,\n    )\n}"]]]],["$","p",{},["注意这里有两层 ",["$","code",{},["ApplyAdjustRules"]],"，第一层应用的是教师在教务系统中录入的单次调课（jwch 库解析出来的 ",["$","code",{},["c.AdjustRules"]],"），第二层才是我们新增的全校性假期调课（前面生成的 ",["$","code",{},["adjustRules"]],"）。"]],["$","p",{},[["$","code",{},["getAdjustRules"]]," 的核心逻辑是对于每条调课记录，遍历该课程的所有排课规则，找出「周次和星期与调课记录的 ",["$","code",{},["from_week"]]," / ",["$","code",{},["from_weekday"]]," 匹配」的那些排课，为其生成一条 ",["$","code",{},["CourseAdjustRule"]],"。这里就正好和前面的日期到周次和星期几的转换遥相呼应，通过预处理减少了在后续阶段的计算量。详细代码请参见 ",["$","a",{"href":"https://github.com/west2-online/fzuhelper-server/blob/404b688e63038c9c34477e978d98a2440a2f21c0/internal/course/service/get_course_list.go#L323-L367","rel":"external nofollow noreferrer"},[["$","code",{},["internal/course/service/get_course_list.go"]]]],"，这里就不再单独贴出来了。"]],["$","h3",{"id":"多级缓存的设计"},["多级缓存的设计"]],["$","p",{},["在 ",["$","code",{},["GetCourseList"]]," 的实现里，有一个特别的设计 —— 数据库和缓存存储的课表内容是不一样的。"]],["$","pre",{},[["$","code",{"class":"hljs go"},[["$","span",{"class":"hljs-comment"},["// 写入数据库存储"]],"\noriginalCourses := pack.BuildCourse(courses)\ns.taskQueue.Add(fmt.Sprintf(",["$","span",{"class":"hljs-string"},["\"putCourse:%s\""]],", stuId), taskqueue.QueueTask{Execute: ",["$","span",{"class":"hljs-function"},[["$","span",{"class":"hljs-keyword"},["func"]],["$","span",{"class":"hljs-params"},["()"]]]]," ",["$","span",{"class":"hljs-type"},["error"]]," {\n    ",["$","span",{"class":"hljs-keyword"},["return"]]," s.putCourseToDatabase(stuId, req.Term, originalCourses)\n}})\n\n",["$","span",{"class":"hljs-comment"},["// ... 应用调课规则 ..."]],"\n\n",["$","span",{"class":"hljs-comment"},["// 写入缓存存储"]],"\ns.taskQueue.Add(courseKey, taskqueue.QueueTask{Execute: ",["$","span",{"class":"hljs-function"},[["$","span",{"class":"hljs-keyword"},["func"]],["$","span",{"class":"hljs-params"},["()"]]]]," ",["$","span",{"class":"hljs-type"},["error"]]," {\n    ",["$","span",{"class":"hljs-keyword"},["return"]]," cache.SetSliceCache(s.cache, s.ctx, courseKey, courses,\n        constants.CourseTermsKeyExpire, ",["$","span",{"class":"hljs-string"},["\"Course.SetCourseCache\""]],")\n}})"]]]],["$","p",{},["数据库存储原始数据是为了保留重新计算的能力。调课规则是随时可能变化的 —— 管理员可能启用新规则，也可能修改或禁用已有规则。如果数据库里存的是某个时间点的处理结果，那么每次规则变更后都需要遍历所有用户的历史数据重新修改并写入，代价极高。而存储原始课表，规则变更后只需要让缓存失效，下次访问时自然会用最新的规则重新计算并回写缓存，做到了数据和规则的解耦。"]],["$","p",{},["缓存存储调课后的数据是为了让 hot path 足够快。对于活跃用户而言，每次打开 App 查看课表都应该是毫秒级响应。如果缓存里存的是原始数据，那么每次命中缓存后还要再走一遍调课信息的匹配逻辑，而调课信息通常是不会频繁变化的，导致白白增加计算开销。所以把已经处理好的结果直接放进缓存，命中时直接返回即可。"]],["$","h2",{"id":"实际效果"},["实际效果"]],["$","p",{},["以文章开头的国庆调课通知为例，来完整地走一遍我们设计的流程。"]],["$","p",{},["教务处通知发出后，",["$","code",{},["syncNoticeTask"]]," 在下一个同步周期抓取到到新通知后，发现标题中含「课程调整」的关键词，随即在后台异步拉取通知正文并调用 ",["$","code",{},["AutoAdjustCourse"]]," 解析，解析后得到的结构化输出如下："]],["$","pre",{},[["$","code",{"class":"hljs json"},[["$","span",{"class":"hljs-punctuation"},["{"]],"\n  ",["$","span",{"class":"hljs-attr"},["\"items\""]],["$","span",{"class":"hljs-punctuation"},[":"]]," ",["$","span",{"class":"hljs-punctuation"},["["]],"\n    ",["$","span",{"class":"hljs-punctuation"},["{"]]," ",["$","span",{"class":"hljs-attr"},["\"from_date\""]],["$","span",{"class":"hljs-punctuation"},[":"]]," ",["$","span",{"class":"hljs-string"},["\"2025-10-01\""]],["$","span",{"class":"hljs-punctuation"},[","]]," ",["$","span",{"class":"hljs-attr"},["\"to_date\""]],["$","span",{"class":"hljs-punctuation"},[":"]]," ",["$","span",{"class":"hljs-string"},["\"\""]]," ",["$","span",{"class":"hljs-punctuation"},["}"]],["$","span",{"class":"hljs-punctuation"},[","]],"\n    ",["$","span",{"class":"hljs-punctuation"},["{"]]," ",["$","span",{"class":"hljs-attr"},["\"from_date\""]],["$","span",{"class":"hljs-punctuation"},[":"]]," ",["$","span",{"class":"hljs-string"},["\"2025-10-02\""]],["$","span",{"class":"hljs-punctuation"},[","]]," ",["$","span",{"class":"hljs-attr"},["\"to_date\""]],["$","span",{"class":"hljs-punctuation"},[":"]]," ",["$","span",{"class":"hljs-string"},["\"\""]]," ",["$","span",{"class":"hljs-punctuation"},["}"]],["$","span",{"class":"hljs-punctuation"},[","]],"\n    ",["$","span",{"class":"hljs-punctuation"